	.string "TUSCANY: I do believe that this\n"
	.string "is the first time we've met?\p"
	.string "I'm TUSCANY of the WEEKDAY FAMILY.\p"
	.string "If you can guess my favorite day,\n"
	.string "I'll give you a reward.$"

